paragraphs.text:
val Text = sc.textFile("C:/Users/Admin/Desktop/büyükv/Admission_Predict_.csv")
case class Admission(SerialNo : Integer, GRE_Score : Integer, TOEFL_Score : Integer, UniversityRating : Integer, SOP : Double, LOR : Double, CGPA : Double, Research : Integer, ChangeofAdmit : Double)

val admission = Text.map(s=>s.split(",")).filter(s=>s(0)!="\"SerialNo\"").map(
    s=>Admission(s(0).toInt, 
            s(1).replaceAll("\"", "").toInt,
            s(2).replaceAll("\"", "").toInt,
            s(3).replaceAll("\"", "").toInt,
            s(4).replaceAll("\"", "").toDouble,
            s(5).replaceAll("\"", "").toDouble,
            s(6).replaceAll("\"", "").toDouble,
            s(7).replaceAll("\"", "").toInt,
            s(8).replaceAll("\"", "").toDouble
        )
)

// convert to DataFrame and create temporal table
admission.toDF().registerTempTable("admission")

%md
## K-Means model

val seed = 5043
val Array(trainData, testData) = finaldf.randomSplit(Array(0.7, 0.3), seed)

val kmeans = new KMeans()
  .setK(2)
  .setFeaturesCol("features")
  .setPredictionCol("prediction")
val model = kmeans.fit(trainData)
model.clusterCenters.foreach(println)

val pDf = model.transform(testData)
pDf.show(truncate = false)
